<p>Sorry to necro; but the Global Occult Coalition maintained a &quot;neutrality&quot; policy with the Foundation.</p>
<p>I put &quot;neutrality&quot; in quotation marks because these agreements have been iffy and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/gdp2-looking-at-the-world-from-a-different-angle">GOC operatives have been involved in questionable incidents which have interfered with Foundation operations.</a></p>
